'''磷化鋁'''（[[英文|英文]]：aluminum phosphide）是一種[[化學式|化學式]]為[[鋁|Al]][[磷|P]]的高毒性[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，可以作為寬[[能隙|能隙]]的[[半導體|半導體]]和[[熏蒸劑|熏蒸劑]]。此無色固體在市面上通常會是灰綠色或是灰黃色粉末則是因為[[水解|水解]]和[[氧化|氧化]]產生了雜質。

==性質==
磷化鋁晶體的顏色通常為暗灰色或暗黃色，具有閃鋅礦晶體結構<ref>{{cite web | author = Van Zeghbroeck, B. J. | title = Bravais Lattices; Zincblende Lattice | publisher = University of Colorado | year = 1997 | url = http://ecee.colorado.edu/~bart/book/bravais.htm | accessdate = 2015-01-19 | archive-date = 2015-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150111211517/http://ecee.colorado.edu/~bart/book/bravais.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在300K的[[晶格常數|晶格常數]]為5.4510Å<ref>{{cite web | title = Lattice Constants | publisher = SiliconFarEast.com | year = 2004 | url = http://www.siliconfareast.com/lattice_constants.htm | accessdate = 10/02/2011 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924101824/http://www.siliconfareast.com/lattice_constants.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在1000 °C（1830°F）以下非常穩定。

磷化鋁與[[水|水]]或[[酸|酸]]反應產生[[磷化氫|磷化氫]]。<ref>{{Holleman&Wiberg}}</ref>

:AlP + 3 H<sub>2</sub>O → Al(OH)<sub>3</sub> + PH<sub>3</sub>
:AlP + 3 H<sup>+</sup> → Al<sup>3+</sup> + PH<sub>3</sub>

==製備==
磷化鋁是由元素間的[[化合反應|化合反應]]所產生的。<ref name=white>{{ cite journal | author = White, W. E.; Bushey, A. H.; Holtzclaw, H. F.; Hengeveld, F. W. | editor = Bailar, J. C. | title = Aluminum Phosphide | journal = Inorganic Syntheses | year = 1953 | volume = 4 | pages = 23–25 | doi = 10.1002/9780470132357.ch7 }}</ref><ref name="ref13">{{cite journal|author = White, W. E.; Bushey, A. H. | title = Aluminum Phosphide – Preparation and Composition | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | doi = 10.1021/ja01238a018 | year = 1944 | volume = 66 | issue = 10 | page = 1666 }}</ref>
: 4Al + P<sub>4</sub> → 4AlP
要避免磷化鋁暴露在任何潮濕的環境下，因為會產生有毒的磷化氫氣體。

==用途==
===農藥===
磷化鋁常常用作[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]、殺鼠劑、或是熏蒸劑，以用來儲存穀物，它可以用來殺死蟲和小型的[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]像是[[鼴|鼴]]或[[齧齒目|齧齒目]]。磷化鋁做成的藥丸常被稱作“麥丸”，通常還包含一些可以增加[[氨|氨]]的化學藥品，這有助於減少自燃或磷化氫氣體[[爆炸|爆炸]]的可能性。

作為殺鼠劑，磷化鋁會被混進齧齒目可能會吃的食物中，在齧齒目的消化系統中，與酸反應產生有毒的磷化氫氣體。

作為熏蒸劑，它可以放進密閉空間，例如[[糧倉|糧倉]]、[[船|船]]、[[飛機|飛機]]、甚至是[[齧齒目|齧齒目]]的巢穴中，產生有毒的[[磷化氫|磷化氫]]氣體，成功達到效果。

===半導體應用===
在[[工業|工業]]中，磷化鋁是一種半導體材料，通常會和其他二元材料形成[[合金|合金]]，以作為[[發光二極體|發光二極體]]（LED），例如：[[鋁鎵磷化銦|鋁鎵磷化銦]]。<ref>{{ cite book | author = Corbridge, D. E. C. | title = Phosphorus: An Outline of its Chemistry, Biochemistry, and Technology | edition = 5th | publisher = Elsevier | location = Amsterdam | year = 1995 | isbn = 0-444-89307-5 }}</ref>

==毒理學==
由于磷化鋁有毒，它曾被用於[[自殺|自殺]]。<ref>{{cite news |title = Millionaire's death sparks poison scare |publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date = 2002-10-10 |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/2314911.stm |accessdate = 2009-04-05 |archive-date = 2012-04-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406051135/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/2314911.stm |dead-url = no }}</ref>另外熏蒸也可能導致意外死亡，[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]<ref>{{cite news |title = Fumes kill two Danes in Jeddah |publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date = 2009-02-24 |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7908102.stm |accessdate = 2009-02-25 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090225112450/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7908102.stm |archivedate = 2009年2月25日 |deadurl = no }}</ref>和[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{cite news |title = Family loses 2nd child in suspected pesticide poisoning |publisher = [[KSL-TV|KSL-TV]] |date = 2010-02-09 |url = http://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=9629232 |accessdate = 2010-02-09 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100211133556/http://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=9629232 |archivedate = 2010年2月11日 |deadurl = no }}</ref> 都曾有過前例，因此有個[[伊朗|伊朗]]法醫組織呼籲禁止磷化鋁作為農藥用途。<ref>{{cite journal|title=A retrospective 7-years study of aluminum phosphide poisoning in Tehran: opportunities for prevention|pages=209–213|issn=1477-0903|journal=Human & Experimental Toxicology|volume=28|issue=4|date=2009-4|doi=10.1177/0960327108097194|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19734272|accessdate=2019-02-13|author=S. Shadnia, G. Sasanian, P. Allami, A. Hosseini, A. Ranjbar, N. Amini-Shirazi, M. Abdollahi|pmid=19734272|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831015605/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19734272|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | last1 = Mehrpour | first1 = O. | last2 = Singh | first2 = S. | title = Rice Tablet Poisoning: A Major Concern in Iranian Population | journal = Human & Experimental Toxicology | volume = 29 | issue = 8 | pages = 701–702 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20097728 | doi = 10.1177/0960327109359643 }}</ref>
在[[西班牙|西班牙]]的[[瓜代拉堡|瓜代拉堡]]，有一個家庭為了做資源回收而把含有磷化鋁的瓶蓋收集放在浴室裡，結果磷化鋁和水反應產生有毒的磷化氫氣體，導致家庭成員全部死亡。<ref>{{cite news|title=La familia de Alcalá de Guadaira murió tras inhalar plaguicida|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/local/sevilla/20140203/54400796210/la-familia-de-alcala-de-guadaira-murio-tras-inhalar-fosfina-de-unos-tapones.html|accessdate=3 February 2014|newspaper=[[La_Vanguardia|La Vanguardia]]|date=3 February 2014|agency=[[Agencia_EFE|Agencia EFE]]|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221134055/http://www.lavanguardia.com/local/sevilla/20140203/54400796210/la-familia-de-alcala-de-guadaira-murio-tras-inhalar-fosfina-de-unos-tapones.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
另外{{le|磷化鋁中毒|Aluminium phosphide poisoning}}也是[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]的一個大問題。<ref name=r4>{{cite journal|pmid=8773034|year=1995|last1=Siwach|first1=SB|last2=Gupta|first2=A|title=The profile of acute poisonings in Harayana-Rohtak Study|volume=43|issue=11|pages=756–9|journal=The Journal of the Association of Physicians of India}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|pmid=10414665|year=1999|last1=Singh|first1=D|last2=Jit|first2=I|last3=Tyagi|first3=S|title=Changing trends in acute poisoning in Chandigarh zone: A 25-year autopsy experience from a tertiary care hospital in northern India|volume=20|issue=2|pages=203–10|journal=The American journal of forensic medicine and pathology|doi=10.1097/00000433-199906000-00019}}</ref>

